The Gautrain bus service has been suspended indefinitely following strike action by some employees. eNCA's Lindokuhle Xulu reports. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Gautrain bus service has been suspended indefinitely following strike action by some employees. The workers are angry over the dismissal of a colleague and have vowed to continue their strike action until he is reinstated. READ: Gautrain Protest | Some drivers refuse to join But their employer Mbombela says due process was followed before the worker was fired. * eNCA's Lindokuhle Xulu reports. Morning, the bus service remains suspended due to illegal protest action. We will keep you updated.